3 months ✨ #tb 

It’s crazy how much changes in 3 short months 🥺. Watching you slowly develop your adorable facial expressions and personality was one of the most rewarding things ❤️. At 3 months we had finally figured out breastfeeding without pain, which was such a relief. Let me know if you guys want to know more about our breastfeeding journey. I have learned SO much! It’s so hard to put into words how much I love you my sweet baby 💕 Looking back at these pictures and seeing how much you’ve grown, makes me emotional 🥹. I can’t believe you’ll be 1 this month! I definitely have to speed up these monthly posts lol.

My baby’s first Christmas 🎄🥰

Wishing everyone a very happy holidays ❤️
The boys ❤️

4 months ✨ 

My beautiful baby girl! 💕 I can’t believe you’ll be one tomorrow! 🥹 Time has gone by way too fast. Omg looking back at that cute gummy smile and those little hands 🥰! At four months you were finally rolling over and a pro at tummy time. Plus you finally learned to smile and would do it all the time! My sweet happy baby ☺️ There’s nothing that brings me more joy than to see that smile ❤️.

Happy 1st birthday to my daughter 🤍 

I’m a little late on the birthday post but on New Year’s Eve, my beautiful baby girl turned one 🥺. Watching you grow has been such a bitter sweet feeling. Time has gone by so fast and it just reminds me how important it is to really cherish and soak in all of these little moments. Every smile, every giggle, every babble, every milestone just fills me with so much joy! You are such a gift baby. Being your mom has been the biggest blessing in my life. I didn’t know how much I needed you until I had you. You are so beautiful, intelligent, strong, determined, silly, funny, and ADORABLE! You are my world. 🤍 Thank you for choosing me. And slow down, ok? 🥺💕

My princess 🤍 

#throwback to her little birthday photoshoot 🥰. That smile just does something to me 🥹💕. I love you forever sweet girl. I still can’t believe you’re already ONE. 

📷: @wrprods @fugate8191

5 months ✨ #tb

Lol my sweet girl is 15 months and I’m just now posting these. I’m so behind but I’ve just been trying to be as present as possible. I plan to post all 12 months. We’ll see how long that takes me lol. Her personality really started coming out at 5 months 🥰.

8 months ✨ #throwback 

At 8 months old my sweet girl was finally pulling herself up and standing on her own 🥹. Baby led weaning was in full swing and avocado was her favorite 🥰. It was her first time sitting in a shopping cart, seeing baby chicks, and spending time with her puppies was one of her favorite things to do lol 💖. I can’t believe how big she is now. Looking back at these pics makes me emotional 🥹.
Merry Christmas from my little family, to yours 🎄❤️🐾

9 months ✨ #throwback 

From starting our little “mommy and me” gym class, to blowing raspberries like a pro 🥲. I can’t believe how fast time has gone by! My baby will be 2 tomorrow 😭. At 9 months old she loved riding in her little bike trailer, bubbles, and Ms.Rachel! It was the only show I didn’t feel guilty letting her watch. 😅❤️

Happy Birthday my beautiful girl 🤍 
I’m so grateful I get to be your mom. Watching you grow and learn these past two years has been so bitter sweet. You are the funniest, sweetest, most adorable little girl both inside and out, and you brighten my day everyday. I’m so glad I get to do life with you 💕. I love you so much baby. Happy birthday and Happy New year my sweet daughter 🤍. 12/31/21
I love celebrating you 🤍
